Description: The ninja war rages on and Naruto is joined by his father in the effort to defeat Obito and Madara.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 66
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Yuma forms the Numbers Club, whose purpose is to find new Numbers Cards and foil the evil plans of Dr. Faker.
Title: YU-GI-OH! ZEXAL, VOL. 5
Author: Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi
Contributor: by Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi

Description: The son of a notorious gangster gets caught in a love triangle with his childhood sweetheart and the daughter of his father’s rival.
Title: NISEKOI: FALSE LOVE, VOL. 4
Author: Naoshi Komi

Description: The origins of the Survey Corps leaders Levi and Erwin are told in this spin–off series.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN: NO REGRETS, VOL. 1
Author: Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama
Contributor: by Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama

Description: Green is sucked into a vortex and only a former enemy can help her escape.
Title: POKEMON ADVENTURES, VOL. 23
Author: Hidenori Kusaka and Satoshi Yamamoto
Contributor: by Hidenori Kusaka and Satoshi Yamamoto

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Set in the same universe as “Negima!,” this series follows Touta, the grandson of Negi Springfield, who becomes a vampire after being mortally wounded.
Title: UQ HOLDER, VOL. 2
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: Kirito has escaped from the virtual reality world of Sword Art Online, but now, he must go inside another game to try and save the woman he loves.
Title: SWORD ART ONLINE: FAIRY DANCE, VOL. 1
Author: Reki Kawahara and Tsubasa Haduki
Contributor: by Reki Kawahara and Tsubasa Haduki

Description: Princess Elizabeth continues her quest to reclaim her kingdom by finding the Seven Deadly Sins, a group of warriors who were wrongly sent into exile and branded as traitors.
Title: SEVEN DEADLY SINS, VOL. 3
Author: Nakaba Suzuki

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, the Titans attack and one of them goes rogue.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 2
Author: Hajime Isayama
